title: Controlled Access Buildings, Window Coverings, BBQ
posting_body: ['The Place You Can Call Home', 'Lake Washington Apartments is a newly remodeled affordable housing community.', 'It features new flooring, new appliances, light fixtures, new plumbing fixtures, new washers/dryers, and new microwaves.', 'Call our friendly leasing team today to find out more.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 40', 'OR Text', '40', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 750 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Carpeting', '- Refrigerator', '- Built-in Microwave', '- Cable Ready', '- Window Coverings', '- Range', '- Individual Climate Control', '- Washer/Dryer', '- Heat (Electric)', 'Community Amenities', '- Free Youth Tutoring and Art Classes', '- Controlled Access Buildings', '- Picnic Area', '- Clubhouse', '- Gated Community', '- 24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', '- Beautiful Courtyard', '- Bicycle Storage', '- Close to everything:', 'Downtown Seattle Airport, Freeways, Major Employers, Grocery Stores, Bank, etc.', '- BBQ', '- Playground', '- Community Vegetable Garden', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly, fees and restrictions apply.', 'Income Requirements:', '*Lake Washington Apartments is a newly remodeled affordable housing community.', 'Income criteria must be met in addition to background, rental and credit history screening.', 'Maximum allowable income for households at 60% of median income level: 1 person- $48,600 ; 2 people- $55,550 ; 3 people- $62,500 ; 4 people- $69,400 ; 5 people- $74,950 ; 6 people- $80,550 ; 7 people- $86,100 ; 8 people- $91,650', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Lake Washington Apartments', '9061 Seward Park S, Seattle, WA, 98118', 'Follow this link to review our screening criteria: <URL>', 'Pt2QoqVkt']
